
Demo of the APIs for the Free Music Archive and The Echo Nest

  http://apidemo.freemusicarchive.org/

  by Mike Adler adler@wfmu.org

1) request FMA api key @ http://freemusicarchive.org/api/agreement
2) request EN api key @ http://developer.echonest.com/account/register
3) put your own api keys into the api_key variables in js/fma.js and js/echonest.js
4) hackety hackety
5) observe the license restrictions of the individual works
6) show your work

This modest player demonstrates how one might use the APIs of the Free
Music Archive and The Echo Nest to create a similarity-based HTML5
audio player.
